day</strong> to <strong>Sunday </strong>from <strong>10:00 – 17:30.</strong><br>Closed: Monday.</p>\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"3cb28f7fa6ea700817e6\\\",\\\"titre_input\\\":\\\"box info2\\\",\\\"name_input\\\":\\\"box-info2\\\",\\\"type_input\\\":\\\"Wysiwyg\\\",\\\"chosen\\\":false,\\\"selected\\\":false,\\\"value\\\":\\\"<p>The last entry is <strong>45 min before closing time.</strong></p>\\\"}]]}]\"', 116, 2),
